sequenceDiagram
    actor A as Admin Keuangan
    participant FP as FormPayroll
    participant PC as PayrollController
    participant DK as DataKaryawan
    participant DP as DataPayroll

    A->>FP: Pilih Karyawan, Input Bonus & Potongan
    A->>FP: Klik Proses()
    FP->>PC: ProsesGaji(Bonus, Potongan)
    PC->>DK: GetGajiStandar(IDKaryawan)
    DK-->>PC: Return: Gaji Pokok & Tunjangan
    PC->>PC: KalkulasiTotalGaji()
    PC->>DP: SimpanDataSlipGaji()
    DP-->>PC: Return: Slip Disimpan
    PC-->>FP: Refresh Tabel & Alert Sukses()
